00:38:18.279 --> 00:38:19.112
right?
- That's right.

00:38:19.112 --> 00:38:20.980
- Okay, so, how do I get one?

00:38:20.980 --> 00:38:23.210
- And that money can be used for politics.

00:38:23.210 --> 00:38:25.150
- Oh great, that's good, too.

00:38:25.150 --> 00:38:26.680
